content:
Integrated Care Management now supports assessments and evidence-based care guidelines from MCG Health. Users can search, administer, and view MCG assessments using the updated Assessment component.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud.

Users need the Care Plans Access permission set license and MCG API credentials to access MCG care guidelines from Health Cloud.

MCG care guidelines help healthcare professionals provide the appropriate care and treatment, resulting in improved outcomes such as reduced length of stay and higher independent quality ratings.

Turn on MCG Care Guidelines in Setup. Create an integration definition for MCG. Then, add the integration definition to the Assessment component, Assessment History component, and IndustriesHCCarePlanManager FlexCard in Lightning App Builder.
title: Enabling MCG Assessments in Health Cloud
